Extract the data matrix from a scalogram

Source: R/fcwtr_scalogram.R
as.matrix.fcwtr_scalogram.Rd

Strips attributes and class from a scalogram object to retrieve a pure matrix.

Usage

# S3 method for class 'fcwtr_scalogram'
as.matrix(x, ...)

Arguments

x

An "fcwtr_scalogram" object resulting from fcwt().

...

additional arguments to be passed to or from methods.

Value

A two dimensional numeric vector, inheriting the S3 class "matrix".

Examples

fcwt(
  sin((1:5000) * 2 * pi * 440 / 44100),
  sample_freq = 44100,
  n_freqs = 10
) |>
  as.matrix()
